lyrics:
I've been searching for my true reflection,
Caught between living a lie and societies perception 
Breaking free from the chains of femininity, finding my way through masculinity,
I’m a self made man, I'm embracing what is true
Looking in the mirror and wishing I was you.

I'm breaking down these walls, 
I won't hide anymore
I'll rise above the judgment, 
breaking stereotypes for sure
This is my journey, my story to unfold,
She becomes He and I'll break the mold
